						<div class="content">
							<h1>Dr. Seamus Clarke</h1>
							<p class="major"> I'm a postdoctoral researcher at the <a href="https://hera.ph1.uni-koeln.de/~walch/Steffi_Walchs_homepage/Main.html">Theoretical Astrophysics group</a> of the University of Cologne. I'm interested in star forming filaments, astrochemistry, synthetic observations and numerical methods.</p>
							
<a href="https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/#search/q=orcid%3A0000-0001-9751-4603&sort=date%20desc%2C%20bibcode%20desc" class="button">Publications</a> 
<!-- <a href="cv/CV.pdf" class="button">CV</a> -->


						</div>
