					</section>


				<!-- Three -->
					<section class="spotlight style1 orient-left content-align-left image-position-center onscroll-image-fade-in" id="first">
						<div class="content">
							<h2>Code development</h2>
							<p> During the course of my research I have developed and contributed to codes which are of use to the wider community:
<ul> 
	<li>I have developed a fully-automated spectral fitting routine, Behind The Spectrum (BTS), which allows for the fitting of entire data cubes of optically thin lines. This code is written as a python module and is open source. </li>
	<li>I have contributed to the code, J-plots, which is a data analysis tool used to quantify the morphology of pixelated structures using their moments. It is written as a python module and is open source
</ul> 
</p>
							<ul class="actions vertical">
								<li><a href="https://github.com/SeamusClarke/BTS" class="button">BTS Github</a></li> <li><a href="https://github.com/SJaffa/Jplots" class="button">J-plots Github</a></li>
							</ul>
						</div>
